thread.title: Sara Drew
thread.title_full: Euroflorist Norge anmeldt av Sara Drew

author: Sara Drew
title: Sara Drew
text: I ordered a plant and chocolates from England for a relative in Norway late one evening. They were delivered by late afternoon the next day. The plant was very pretty and healthy and the chocolates were delicious. This was an excellent service at a very competitive price.
